com.cubeia.firebase.api.action.visitor
Interface MttActionVisitor

All Superinterfaces:
Visitor
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractActionHandler, AbstractTableActionHandler, DefaultActionVisitor, DefaultGameActionHandler, DefaultMttActionVisitor, MttActionHandler, MttDefaultVisitor, MttTableActionHandler, StandardTableActionHandler
public interface MttActionVisitor
extends Visitor

Will contain a "visit" method for each action type in the system. A default implementation will be provided for each action in the DefaultVisitor which will do nothing.
